author: Charlie Spiering, Charlie Spiering
title: Donald Trump Casts Doubt on China's Coronavirus Numbers
description: "You don't know what the numbers are in China," Trump said to reporters during the White House press briefing on Thursday evening.
content:
President Donald Trump cast doubt Thursday on the official coronavirus numbers coming out of China.
“You don’t know what the numbers are in China,” Trump said to reporters during the White House press briefing on Thursday evening.
